snippet `lr([\)\]\>\}vV])` "[G] Left-right" A
`` trans = {")": ["(", ")"], "]": ["[", "]"], ">": ["<", ">"], "}": ["{", "}"], "v": ["\\lvert", "\\rvert"], "V": ["\\lVert", "\\rVert"]}
rv = "\\left" + trans[m[1]][0] + " $1 " + "\\right" + trans[m[1]][1] ``
endsnippet

